cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.CY, cs.SE 

The paper focuses on the security issues in the 5G network slicing environment, which is related to cryptography and network security. Therefore, cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the application scenarios and performance analysis, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also mentions the use of Raspberry Pi to simulate the interprocess communication, which is related to cyber-physical systems (cs.CY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
